    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a major project. The engine currently has a heavy knock and requires a complete overhaul, and the transmission is slipping significantly in higher gears. Externally, there is noticeable rust on the quarter panels and several deep scratches and dents throughout the body. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It is not currently in drivable condition for long distances and will likely need to be towed.",
