    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved? This car has been my super reliable companion and is still in great shape for its next adventure! It runs smoothly and has been well-maintained over the years. It's the perfect fit for anyone needing a solid, dependable vehicle without that 'brand new' price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're really going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS timing. This unit is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels through the factory M-Variable lock differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The suspension retains its telepathic feedback thanks to refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While showing honest patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical integrity remains sharp, offering the visceral, naturally aspirated performance that defined an era of BMW M-division engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for pickup.",
